Waterford foods talks with Avonmore . Irish food group Waterford Foods Plc said it that it has received an approach from Avonmore Food Plc which may or may not lead to an offer . Waterford said in a statement that if an offer was received it would be evaluated in due course . Industry sources said this appeared to be a renewal of merger attempts which were aborted in 1991 . Further details were not immediately available . Waterford said in one year ago that market conditions were depressed and it was considering a merger , partnership or strategic alliance . - - Dublin Newsroom + 353 - 1 - 6613377 
